habiliar no firebase
copiar os ids do face no fire
copiar a url do fire no face
ionic cordova plugin add cordova-plugin-facebook4 --variable APP_ID="726987884307443" --variable APP_NAME="myApplication"
npm install --save @ionic-native/facebook
